data.description: Welcome to this charming farm house on 3.83 acres of land with no covenants! The possibilities are endless with outbuildings & pasture that could house chickens, horses or goats. You'll fall in love with the original woodwork and character of this home, but appreciate the modern updates that make it move-in ready. This farmhouse has been completely remodeled from top to bottom, offering peace of mind to its new owners. Enjoy a serene country lifestyle with an easy commute to the metro. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own a piece of rural paradise!
